---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Accessibility Statement">
  <article class="panel">
    <h1>Accessibility statement</h1>
    <p>
      This site targets WCAG 2.2 AAA criteria wherever technically feasible. We prioritize semantic HTML,
      keyboard support, high contrast, visible focus, and reduced-motion compatibility.
    </p>
    <h2>Implemented controls</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Landmarks and heading hierarchy on every page.</li>
      <li>Skip link and keyboard navigable controls.</li>
      <li>Color contrast tuned for light and dark themes.</li>
      <li>Accessible form labels, validation hints, and live status region in API tester.</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
